translations: v.形成锯齿状；[印刷]缩排；缩进（indent 的三单形式）
n.锯齿形缺口；首行缩排（indent 的复数）

sentences.sentence: The sea indents the western coast of the island.
sentences.translation: 大海把岛屿西部海岸线切成锯齿状。

sentences.sentence: Trust newlines and indents to keep my code not only structured but running?
sentences.translation: 让我相信换行和缩进能保证代码的结构和运行？

sentences.sentence: Use the indents page to set indents in the right and left margins of the section.
sentences.translation: 使用缩进页设置区域右边界和左边界的缩进。
